596
01:13:04,953 --> 01:13:06,288
Antar ke Gwangju.

597
01:13:06,371 --> 01:13:08,206
Kau harus ke terminal.

598
01:13:09,124 --> 01:13:12,210
- Kalau begitu, antar ke terminal.
- Baik.

599
01:13:22,637 --> 01:13:23,471
Taksi!

600
01:13:25,390 --> 01:13:26,224
Taksi!

601
01:13:37,861 --> 01:13:39,696
- Gwangju!
